Package de.dedede.model.data.dtos

Class AttributeDto

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.dedede.model.data.dtos.AttributeDto
  • public class AttributeDto
extends java.lang.Object
    This DTO (data transfer object) is responsible for aggregating and encapsulating data about the attribute of the medium for transfer.

    See the ApplicationDao class to which this DTO is passed.

    Author:
    Sergei Pravdin
